description: Record to support submission of GeneRIFs for a gene not in Gene (Achromobacter lunatus; Bacillus campestris; Bacterium campestre; Phytomonas campestris; Pseudomonas campestris; Xanthomonas campestris var. aberrans; Xanthomonas campestris var. armoraceae.  Use when strain, subtype, isolate, etc. is unspecified, or when different from all specified ones in Gene.).
